    =&\frac{1}{2}\int_{-1}^1\para{ue^u-ue^{-u}}\,du=\frac12\intvert{\para{ue^u-e^u+ue^{-u}+e^{-u}}}_{-1}^1=2e^{-1}.
\end{split}\]

